Compute Between se's

Source: R/toolbox.R
between.Rd

Between SEs

between(bymro)

Arguments

bymro

a bymro object

Value

something about between.

Author

Junjie Zheng

Examples

mr <- iNZightMR(online ~ onlinegame + onlinevideo + onlinemusic,
    data = census.at.school.5000)
(bt <- between(byMRO(mr, ~gender, mroPara)))
